{"tid":1402473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家唔好再畀人影張相／屌兩句就失控","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:15:47.000Z","uid":129622,"like":58,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3f71b263d65b7da705129b1420f9139b5f8927","tid":1402473,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"講左好多次 鏡頭係避唔到 <br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">面對黑警已經精神繃緊 仲要擔心四面八方有人影你相？</span><br />\n有人拎起電話就觸動到你 即刻跳起插佢 <br />\n結果引起唔少紛爭 如果係誤會已經好麻煩 驚動到其他示威者好易又開拖<br />\n每次遊行集會都少不免出現以上情況 唔係次次有人調庭 搞到好難收科<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n今日一隻廢老影相 有幾位義士已經忍唔住開波 <br />\n在場有其他義士調庭 廢老屌埋人老母義士就忍唔住出拳 最後近十人加入<br />\n<br />\n我地既武力係用係對抗獨裁政府上面 而唔係盲毛廢老<br />\n咁樣唔係吞聲忍氣 而係真係唔應該花精神處理呢種廢老 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">成日話打遊擊既心態就係用最低成本去增加黑警工作<br />\n點可能到轉頭人地用部手提機話影張相就挑釁到我地 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ed28e2a251a25b0d256a855ba116561219cd3451","tid":1402473,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b382b0539ee4ed80feb41c7b60aa3ab461885bd","tid":1402473,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"食宵夜果陣聽到隔離呀叔俾左3個寶貴意見<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dvjseS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dvjseS</a>"},{"pid":"80dddc457ec77a31689867aa69850de79a7da6c6","tid":1402473,"uid":33875,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"發夢經常聽到 ：「xxxxx，叫我點冷靜啊 ？」<br />\n<br />\n我明白企得前都背負好多原因，但企喺前線唔能夠冷靜理性去處理每個問題、下每一個決定，其實對自己或者對身邊既戰友都唔係一件好事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"3340820069d4bf140e5c2dbaa153a4e417414f3d","tid":1402473,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4753075b3c3610d42cfc0522af970ecb148a6d3","tid":1402473,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"我宣佈最強既裝備係 「街 坊 裝」 ！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1402170/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1402170/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"68588291e74bdb3ec0b0845c43e3081a585b165b","tid":1402473,"uid":238551,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:36:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afa2891ad8d5fd08829af0fb868979112341427a","tid":1402473,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68588291e74bdb3ec0b0845c43e3081a585b165b","tid":1402473,"uid":238551,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:36:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"有幾多政權，會出動到人民互鬥，抹黑示威者呢d爛仔招數?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1398046/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1398046/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n你自個出過Post講<em><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>挑撥人民之間感情（黃藍）真係好賤</ins></span></em><br />\n<br />\n我地就係唔應該咁容易被挑撥<br />\n唔係講緊打佢有冇問題 <br />\n而係一開始只係影張相就被挑撥到 <br />\n其實並唔係一件好事<br />\n<br />\n一來會誤傷無辜遊客<br />\n二來令示威者精神繃緊"},{"pid":"115dae9c2337ce99ec68f7a733de2d12bb7bd865","tid":1402473,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"蘋果：黃大仙黑警宿舍 有家屬持木棍驅趕街坊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1402505/page/1\" ta